 2011-12342011-10-20,  ,  ,  ,  HRSDC
ActEmployment Insurance Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Employment Insurance Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the EMPLOYMENT INSURANCE REGULATIONS, in order to allow claimants to combine the specific exceptions of visiting a seriously ill immediate family member and attending the funeral of that same family member. Technical amendments are being made to correct discrepancies between the English and the French wording of sections of the Regulations.
